nowplaying-sdl (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Major release 1.0.0
  * Added screensaver functionality with backlight control
  * Screensaver dims display after inactivity, turns off when playback stops
  * Configurable brightness levels and timeouts
  * Touch events reset screensaver timer
  * Screensaver keeps display on during playback
  * Increased button sizes for better touch usability (120-130px)
  * Fixed button icon scaling to match button size
  * Optimized button spacing for better layout
  * Improved touch event handling and logging
  * Fixed logging configuration to properly show INFO level logs

 -- HiFiBerry <info@hifiberry.com>  Sun, 08 Dec 2024 12:00:00 +0000

nowplaying-sdl (0.3.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Added circular layout mode for circular displays
  * New --circle command-line argument
  * Circle mode uses circular area based on minimum screen dimension
  * All UI elements (cover, title, artist, buttons) fit within circular area

 -- HiFiBerry <info@hifiberry.com>  Mon, 02 Dec 2024 16:00:00 +0000

nowplaying-sdl (0.2.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Removed system service dependency (user services cannot depend on system services)
  * Application handles audiocontrol connection automatically with retry logic

 -- HiFiBerry <info@hifiberry.com>  Mon, 02 Dec 2024 15:30:00 +0000

nowplaying-sdl (0.2.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fixed systemd service to install as user service instead of system service
  * Added dependency on audiocontrol.service in systemd unit
  * Added postinst script for proper user service enablement

 -- HiFiBerry <info@hifiberry.com>  Mon, 02 Dec 2024 15:00:00 +0000

nowplaying-sdl (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Added AudioControl API integration for live now-playing data
  * Implemented cover art download and caching system
  * Added configuration file support (/etc or ~/.config)
  * Added systemd user service for automatic startup
  * Added --demo mode for testing without API
  * Fixed cover art display with proper field name mapping
  * Improved background polling with thread-based updates
  * Removed debug code and print statements

 -- HiFiBerry <info@hifiberry.com>  Mon, 02 Dec 2024 14:00:00 +0000

nowplaying-sdl (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * SDL2-based now playing display
  * Support for screen rotation (0, 90, 180, 270 degrees)
  * Touch-friendly button controls
  * Album cover art display
  * Material Design icons

